- Initial stalemate test setup detected checking because the Red Rook was positioned on the same column with no pieces in between. Fixed by placing a blocking Red Pawn on that column to block Kings direct facing and checking.
- Prompt suggestions: - Maintain a pre-mocked DOM testing environment template in projects to streamline server-side testing of client-side JS.
